Package com.seailz.discordjv.model.interaction.reply

Class InteractionMessageResponse

java.lang.Object
com.seailz.discordjv.model.interaction.reply.InteractionMessageResponse
All Implemented Interfaces:
Compilerable, InteractionReply
public class InteractionMessageResponse extends Object implements InteractionReply
Represents a InteractionCallbackType 4 interaction response. This includes some message info.

Note: This is an internal class and should not be used by the end user.

Since:
1.0
Author:
